messageBody:
Hi,
Iam trying to test the WebServices through Junit. Iam using Glue to
extract wsdl2java.

while running my test textui is running fine but when Iam trying to
run the same test with swingui.TestRunner it is saying the "license
key is invalid"

D:\WebServices>java junit.swingui.TestRunner SimpleTest
[STARTUP] license key is invalid
[STARTUP] place a valid license xml file in class path or contact
webMethods sal
es to arrange a new license

D:\WebServices>java junit.textui.TestRunner SimpleTest
.[STARTUP] Glue Standard 5.0.2 build 77 (c) 2001-2004 webMethods, Inc.

Time: 3.516

OK (1 test)

How we can handle this exception ? and I would like to know the
approch for testing WebServices ?

thanks,
Raju
